  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6430276">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6430276/" class="title-link">聊表敬意</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6430276"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1727444/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1727444-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1727444/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Ghost</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-23 22:10:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6430276_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我不是一个“一切都是以前好”主义者。我坚信，现在比以前好多了，未来还会更好，而坏人在任何时代的比例都是一个宇宙常数，不以人的意志为转移。然而，很多年前，读到茨威格的《昨日的世界》，开头那段热情洋溢的茨老师式一波三折的咏叹调还是让我多少有些动容，“倘若要我今...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6430276/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">23有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6430276_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6430276_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6178391">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6178391/" class="title-link">简评章骞五年磨一剑之大作《无畏之海》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6178391"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/75681101/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u75681101-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/75681101/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">youngyang_xzz</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-23 17:42:19</span>
</div>

